---
title: Sweet-Soy Eggplant, Beef & Cucumber Slaw with Sesame Dressing & Crispy Shallots
description: Eggplant roasted in the oven has to be one of our favourite veggies. The sweet soy seasoning gives it a special boost of flavour and the refreshing cucumber slaw, drizzled over with sesame dressing, tastes divine.
